    "(a) (b) Our learning result demonstrates how asynchronously interacting p-bits can creatively combine with existing CMOS technology.",
    "Scaled and integrated implementations of this concept could lead to a resurgence in training powerful DBMs 58.",
    "Given our prior results stressing how the quality of randomness can play a critical role in probabilistic inference and learning, it is beneficial to perform precise, quantitative comparisons with the various digital PRNGs we built in hardware FPGAs with sMTJ-based p-bits 15.",
    "Note that for this comparison, we do not consider augmented CMOS p-bits, but directly compare sMTJ-based mixed signal p-bits with their digital counterparts (see Supplementary Note XVI for details on projections of integrated implementations using sMTJ-based mixed signal p-bits).",
    "Moreover, instead of benchmarking the voltage comparator-based pbit circuit shown in Fig. 1 or other types of spin-orbit torque-based p-bits 3, 59, we benchmark the 3T/1MTJ-based p-bit first reported in ref."
  ]
